song.title: ThisIsWhatHappensWhenRamsDoesNotCloseTheUpload
song.info:
Entry for the Scenecompos #32 - AHX Compo. Placed 19th.
Artist Comment: Look! The upload button is still there, even though the compo deadline has passed!
Artist Production Notes: Screwdriver, sledgehammer and a cork from a wine bottle.
Download in the [url=http://compos.scenemusic.net/dl/36_complete.tar.gz]compopack[/url]
